{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 751144, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 156544, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "过来人告诉你，缓考需要校医院或北医三院诊断证明（因病休息时间覆盖考试时间），在教学门户上下载缓考申请表，填写并让院系教务盖章，教学副院长/副系主任签字，再交到注册中心办理。\n缓考一时爽，大四火葬场。", "timestamp": 1608564390, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 751155, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 156544, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "能不缓考尽量不缓考", "timestamp": 1608564480, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 751167, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 156544, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "除非确定要挂，不然尽量不要缓考。逃得了一时逃不了一世。", "timestamp": 1608564580, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 751331, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 156544, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 可以加联系方式聊一下吗", "timestamp": 1608565842, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 751337, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 156544, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "cz大一期末突然长水痘，还好只缓了一门，尽量少缓考叭", "timestamp": 1608565960, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 751350, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 156544, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 缓考之后是要重修还是重新考试，分数会怎么算啊", "timestamp": 1608566039, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 751429, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 156544, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 就在这聊吧，有什么想问的都可以问", "timestamp": 1608566759, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 751950, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 156544, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "缓考一般情况是成绩单记I（incomplete） 第二年跟随下一届考试 平时成绩可以保留\n个人建议不是必要情况就别办缓考 cz大三上考试周骨折做手术 缓考了4门专业大课 惨", "timestamp": 1608572335, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 754519, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 156544, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 必须校医院or北医三院吗？alice了解心理原因缓考吗", "timestamp": 1608631537, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 761374, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 156544, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 请问考期医生容易开病假条吗 一般什么病能开下来（最好是两三天的假）", "timestamp": 1608728015, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 7, "pid": 156544, "reply": 10, "tag": null, "text": "请问从哪里可以看到申请缓考的说明啊", "timestamp": 1608564228, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1608728015, "url": "", "vote": {}}}